        {
            "title": "宇樹科技傳與阿里巴巴合作出海",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地傳媒報道，宇樹科技與阿里巴巴(09988)正籌備合作出海，將在4月中旬公布詳情。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260323_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">報道指，智能機械人製造商宇樹科技的最新機器人R1，現身阿里巴巴的西溪園區，據內部消息，雙方正籌備一個出海合作項目，預計4月中旬在深圳舉辦的一場品牌大會上正式發表。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另有消息稱，該項目或將落地阿里旗下跨境電商平台速賣通，速賣通正與多個品牌合作，推出定制的深度出海方案和戰略級項目，意在為更多中國品牌、尤其是天貓品牌提供出海解決方案。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851093-%e5%ae%87%e6%a8%b9%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e5%82%b3%e8%88%87%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c%e5%87%ba%e6%b5%b7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/Unitree-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 12:00:50",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "外區客鍾情物業位處名校網  斥778萬購西半山興漢大廈3房戶",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">利嘉閣地產西半山-寶翠園分行新近促成西半山興漢大廈低層D室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約727方呎，採3房間隔，外望城市景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">業主原以850萬元放售，經誠意磋商後以略低於市價778萬元成交，折合實用面積呎價約10702元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">原業主在1985年以約48.8萬元買入單位，持貨至今易手，帳面獲利逾729萬元，期內物業升值近15倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該物業現時有約10個單位放盤，入場售價約由600萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851074-%e5%a4%96%e5%8d%80%e5%ae%a2%e9%8d%be%e6%83%85%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%ad%e4%bd%8d%e8%99%95%e5%90%8d%e6%a0%a1%e7%b6%b2-%e6%96%a5778%e8%90%ac%e8%b3%bc%e8%a5%bf%e5%8d%8a%e5%b1%b1%e8%88%88%e6%bc%a2%e5%a4%a7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 11:55:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股收跌  深股跌穿14000關",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股半日收跌，深股稍微跌穿14000，兩市成交合計14260.74億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指半日收報3965，跌29點或0.73%，今早以3967點開市，跌27點或0.69%，最低報3961點，跌34點或0.85%，為上午低位，其後跌幅收窄，最高見3979，跌16點或0.4%，半日成交6007.59億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指半日收報13999，跌42點或0.31%，今早開市報13928點，亦跌114點或0.81%，最低見13891，挫151點或1.08%，為半日低位，中段見14058，升16點或0.11%，為半日高位，半日成交8253.15億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數半日跌29點或0.64%，創業板指數半日報3325，跌22點或0.67%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">霍爾木茲海峽再度關閉，中東局勢再度緊張，亞洲股市回調。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15850986-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e7%a9%bf14000%e9%97%9c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-10.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 11:37:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
